Residents of Obot Akara LGA in Akwa Ibom State have raised an alarm after being cut off from the rest of the state following the collapse of Mbiaso-Ikot Ukpong Bridge in the community. The bridge collapsed in the early hours of today August 10, after a cement truck rode on it for delivery. Relevant authorities have been called upon to come to the aid of the community. Here are photos below; ~